1. *Ljubazni* prodavac mi je ponudio pomoć. (The *kind* salesperson offered me help.)
2. Hvala na *ljubaznosti* koju ste mi pružili. (Thank you for the *kindness* you have shown me.)
3. Oni su bili vrlo *ljubazni* prema meni tokom celog boravka. (They were very *kind* to me throughout my stay.)
4. Nisam očekivao da će biti tako *ljubazna* prema meni. (I didn't expect her to be so *kind* to me.)
5. Da li možete biti malo *ljubazniji* prema svojim kolegama? (Can you be a little *kinder* to your colleagues?)
6. Potrebno je biti *ljubazan* prema svima bez obzira na njihovu poziciju. (It's important to be *kind* to everyone regardless of their position.)
7. Molim vas, budite *ljubazni* i odgovorite mi na ovo pitanje. (Please be *kind* and answer my question.)
8. Naš hotel je poznat po svom *ljubaznom* osoblju. (Our hotel is known for its *friendly* staff.)
9. *Ljubaznošću* ovog profesora, shvatio sam gradivo. (Thanks to the *kindness* of this professor, I understood the material.)
10. Bilo bi *ljubazno* od vas da mi javite da li ćete doći. (It would be *kind* of you to let me know if you're coming.)